title: OU Set to Battle No. 9 Texas Tech in Lubbock - University of Oklahoma - Soonersports.com
content: OU Set to Battle No. 9 Texas Tech in Lubbock - University of Oklahoma  Soonersports.com
description: NORMAN – Oklahoma (14-13, 4-10 Big 12) continues its two-game road swing at No. 11 Texas Tech (21-6, 10-4 Big 12) Tuesday, Feb. 22.
